Control Statement is the Statement that control the flow of execution of Program

/* Types of Control Statement */\

a. Decision Making Statement -> that decide which block of code will be execute
   if-else 
   switch

b. Iteration Statement -> How number of times a block of code will be executed
   for loop
   while loop
   do-while loop

c. Jump Statement -> transfer the execution control from one point to another in the program
   break -> terminate the loop and give the control to next instruction
   continue -> skip the rest iteration and go to next iteration